title: Simple Jumps
briefDescription: A very simple parkour map.Simple jumps is a fun, easy parkour map, that will test your abilities at parkour and provide hours of entertainment....

crawledImageUrls.text:
A very simple parkour map.
Simple jumps is a fun, easy parkour map, that will test your abilities at parkour and provide hours of entertainment.
This map took about 3 months to build, and 4 days to playtest. Built completely by DaBoopIsALie, and tested by me as well. If you want to set a record for this map, check out r/DaBoopIsALie on reddit and provide video evidence and you may find yourself on the leaderboard.
This is a parkour map that gets harder and harder as it goes along, using many different and new types of parkour to test the true parkour skill of anyone, even the best Minecraft players.
The map is indeed possible, so if you cannot do a jump, just keep on trying and good luck.
This map consists of, until its opened, 10 levels, each getting harder and harder as they go on, and each present a new challenge, and improve upon earlier challenges, keeping the jumps on the edge of possible and impossible.
This is my first map, but it will not be the last in the story, only getting harder and harder from here.

title: Hide And Go Edawg (Updated) 1.16 Bedrock
briefDescription: This was fun Hide and Seek map me my cousins worked on. It has tones hidden secrets and areas to explore. Plus lots of parkour ...

crawledImageUrls.text: This was fun Hide and Seek map me my cousins worked on. It has tones hidden secrets and areas to explore. Plus lots of parkour and some other mini games too like spleef, pig racing,shoot the minecart, Slap them off, connect 4, noughts and crosses (Tic Tac Toe), Foot Race, Isolation, Build Battle and Rock Paper Scissors.

Hide And Go Edawg
The reason why it is called hide and go edawg instead of hide and seek is because we originally built a similar map on a server called edawg and played it there (Server Ip for Java Players: EDAWG878.COM).

Rules of Hide and Go Edawg
Be welcome to play around with certain rules
Main rules of Hide and Go Edawg:
1)No ones allowed to break or place blocks in a match
2)Hider starts game with a knockback wooden sword (If you want to get rid of nametags you can effect the hider with invisibility and give them leather armour or trust the seekers to turn off nametags in their settings)
3)Seeker starts game with Enchanted diamond sword and armour, and a Glistering Melon (Glistering Melons can be used to enter the theme park)
4)Once a hider is found unless there is no hiders left that hider must become seeker.
5)If a Hider dies not from a seeker or a seekers wolf, they must tp back to the hider area (They do not become seeker)
6)The seeker goal is to kill all hiders
7)The Hider goal is to survive for as long as possible, but they can do one of these things.
1.Just Hide
2.Try and visit every area
3.kill a non afk seeker
Other gamemodes:
1.Try Playing the game but give every player and elytra and fireworks
2. Instead of hide and seek try doing survival games by having everyone tp to hider area and locate items around the map. (Have a time at the start where no one can pvp)
3.Try some of the minigames that can be located in spawn

briefDescription: Play with your friends and try to be the first who claimed 5 points to win .You can play from 1 to 30 players without any lag or ...

crawledImageUrls.text:
Play with your friends and try to be the first who claimed 5 points to win .
You can play from 1 to 30 players without any lag or a problem>scoreboard .
And you can play with texture packs and addons with no issues because the map only made with less than 20 commands to evict the lag .
What is this ?
This map is a mulitplayer and solo parkour map .
The map recreate a random possible parkour every time you pass a level .
The map can handle over 20 players moving in the same time because it only has less than 20 command block .
How I play ?

When all players are ready to start click on the ?Start game? button and the map will make a random parkour in 0.3 second after that you and your friends will get teleported to the parkour and try to beat it first to beat get a point after that the map will keep creating random parkours until someone claim 5 points .
When you claim 5 points you?ll win after that the map may take from 3 to 6 seconds to reboot himself .
You can play the map over 100 time without any problems .
